{{short description|Educatonal award in the fields of limnology and oceanography}} {{Use mdy dates|date=May 2018}} The '''Ramón Margalef Award for Excellence in Education''' was launched in 2008 by the [[Association for the Sciences of Limnology and Oceanography]] to recognize innovations and excellence in teaching and mentoring students in the fields of [[limnology]] and [[oceanography]]. Criteria for the award requires "adherence to the highest standards of excellence" in pedagogy as well as verification that the teaching techniques have furthered the field of aquatic science.<ref name="ASLO2018" >{{cite web|title=Ramón Margalef Award for Excellence in Education|url=https://aslo.org/p/cm/ld/fid=1069|website=ASLO|publisher=Association for the Sciences of Limnology and Oceanography|accessdate=May 12, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180512164818/https://aslo.org/p/cm/ld/fid=1069|archivedate=May 12, 2018|location=Washington, D. C.|date=2018}}</ref><ref name="Palmer 2016" >{{cite web|last1=Palmer|first1=Sally|title=Ken Dunton receives prestigious 2016 Ramón Margalef Award for Excellence in Education|url=https://utmsi.utexas.edu/blog/entry/margalefaward|website=Marine Science Institute|publisher=The University of Texas|accessdate=May 12, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180512165057/https://utmsi.utexas.edu/blog/entry/margalefaward|archivedate=May 12, 2018|location=Port Aransas, Texaas|date=January 13, 2016}}</ref> The award is not affiliated with the [[Ramon Margalef Prize in Ecology]], often referred to as the Ramon Margalef Award, given by the [[Generalitat de Catalunya]] in Barcelona.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Blackman|first1=Christine|title=Paul Ehrlich receives Ramon Margalef Award for lifetime achievements in ecology|url=https://news.stanford.edu/news/2009/august3/ehrlich-margalef-award-080709.html|accessdate=May 12, 2018|publisher=''Stanford Report''|date=August 7, 2009|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311121954/https://news.stanford.edu/news/2009/august3/ehrlich-margalef-award-080709.html|archivedate=March 11, 2018|location=Stanford, California}}</ref> The award has been presented annually since 2009.<ref name="ASLO2018" />
